  "keyFeatures": [
    "CPU-optimized predictive modeling and risk stratification for hospital data",
    "Real-time anomaly detection with hardware-constrained early warning system",
    "Streaming inference with configurable latency and throughput optimization",
    "ONNX model export for cross-platform deployment",
    "Deterministic reproducibility and comprehensive benchmarking",
    "Hardware profiling with memory and compute budget constraints",
    "End-to-end pipeline from data ingestion to deployment monitoring"
